\c 6
\s Umlayo omayelana lomNaziri
\p
\v 1 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 2 Tshono ebantwaneni bakoIsrayeli uthi kubo: Owesilisa loba owesifazana, uba ezehlukanisela ukuthembisa isithembiso\x + Levi 27.2.\x* somNaziri\x + Gen. 49.26. Hlu. 13.5. Seb. 21.23. Roma 1.1.\x*, ukuze azehlukanisele iN\nd kosi\nd*,
\v 3 uzazehlukanisa lewayini lokunathwayo okulamandla, anganathi iviniga lewayini, leviniga lokunathwayo okulamandla, anganathi lamhluzi wezithelo zevini, angadli izithelo zevini ezimanzi lezomileyo\x + Amos 2.12. Luka 1.15.\x*.
\v 4 Zonke insuku zokuzehlukanisela kwakhe kayikudla okolutho olwenziwe ngevini lewayini, kusukela enhlamvini kusiya emakhasini.
\v 5 Zonke insuku zesithembiso sokuzehlukanisela kwakhe impuco kayiyikudlula phezu kwekhanda lakhe\x + Hlu. 13.5; 16.17; 1 Sam. 1.11.\x*; kuze kugcwaliseke insuku zokuzehlukanisela kwakhe iN\nd kosi\nd* uzakuba ngcwele, ayekele izihluthu zenwele zekhanda lakhe zikhule\x + Hez. 44.20.\x*.
\v 6 Zonke insuku azehlukanisele iN\nd kosi\nd* ngazo kayikuya esidunjini\x + Levi 21.11; Nani 19.11,16.\x*.
\v 7 Kayikuzingcolisa ngoyise, langonina, ngomfowabo, langodadewabo, uba befile, ngoba ukwehlukaniselwa uNkulunkulu wakhe kuphezu kwekhanda lakhe\x + Levi 21.1,2,11.\x*.
\v 8 Zonke insuku zokuzehlukanisela kwakhe ungcwele eN\nd kosi\nd*ni.
\v 9 Uba-ke ofayo ejunywa masinyane yikufa phansi kwakhe, usengcolise ikhanda lokuzehlukanisela kwakhe\x + Isa. 29.5; 30.13.\x*, uzaphuca ikhanda lakhe ngosuku lokuhlanjululwa kwakhe, uzaliphuca ngosuku lwesikhombisa\x + 6.18.\x*.
\v 10 Langosuku lwesificaminwembili uzaletha amajuba amabili loba amaphuphu amabili enkwilimba kumpristi emnyango wethente lenhlangano\x + Levi 5.7; 14.22; 15.14,29.\x*.
\v 11 Lompristi uzanikela enye ibe ngumnikelo wesono, lenye ibe ngumnikelo wokutshiswa, amenzele inhlawulo yokuthula, ngoba wonile ngesidumbu. Njalo uzangcwelisa ikhanda lakhe ngalona lolosuku,
\v 12 azehlukanisele iN\nd kosi\nd* insuku zokuzehlukanisela kwakhe, alethe iwundlu elilomnyaka owodwa libe ngumnikelo wecala\x + Levi 5.2,6.\x*; kodwa insuku zakuqala zizakuwa, ngoba ukuzehlukanisela kwakhe kungcolisiwe.
\p
\v 13 Lalo ngumlayo womNaziri ngosuku lapho insuku zokuzehlukanisela kwakhe sezigcwalisekile. Uzaletha lokhu emnyango wethente lenhlangano\x + Seb. 21.26.\x*,
\v 14 anikele umnikelo wakhe eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, iwundlu elilodwa elilomnyaka owodwa elingelasici libe ngumnikelo wokutshiswa, lewundlukazi elilodwa elilomnyaka owodwa elingelasici libe ngumnikelo wesono\x + Levi 4.32.\x*, lenqama ibenye engelasici ibe yiminikelo yokuthula\x + Levi 3.6.\x*,
\v 15 lesitsha sezinkwa ezingelamvubelo, amaqebelengwana empuphu ecolekileyo ehlanganiswe lamafutha\x + Levi 2.4.\x*, lezinkwana eziyizipatalala ezingelamvubelo ezinindwe ngamafutha\x + Eks. 29.2.\x*, lomnikelo wazo wokudla leminikelo yazo yokunathwayo\x + 15.5,7,10.\x*.
\v 16 Njalo umpristi uzakusondeza phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, anikele umnikelo wakhe wesono\x + 6.14.\x* lomnikelo wakhe wokutshiswa\x + 6.14.\x*.
\v 17 Lenqama uzayinikela ibe ngumhlatshelo weminikelo yokuthula\x + 6.14.\x* eN\nd kosi\nd*ni kanye lesitsha sezinkwa ezingelamvubelo; lompristi uzanikela umnikelo wakhe wokudla lomnikelo wakhe wokunathwayo\x + 6.15.\x*.
\v 18 UmNaziri uzaphuca-ke ikhanda lokuzehlukanisela kwakhe emnyango wethente lenhlangano, athathe inwele zekhanda lokuzehlukanisela kwakhe, azifake emlilweni ongaphansi komhlatshelo weminikelo yokuthula\x + Seb. 21.24.\x*.
\v 19 Lompristi uzathatha umkhono ophekiweyo wenqama, leqebelengwana elilodwa elingelamvubelo esitsheni, lesinkwana esisodwa esiyisipatalala esingelamvubelo\x + 1 Sam. 2.15.\x*, akubeke ezandleni zomNaziri esephucile ukuzehlukanisela kwakhe\x + Eks. 29.23,24.\x*,
\v 20 umpristi akuzunguze-ke kube ngumnikelo wokuzunguzwa phambi kweN\nd kosi\x + Eks. 29.24.\x*\nd*; kungcwele kumpristi, kanye lesifuba esizunguziweyo kanye lomlenze wokuphakanyiswa\x + 5.25. Eks. 29.27,28.\x*. Emva kwalokhu umNaziri usenganatha iwayini.
\v 21 Lo ngumlayo womNaziri othembise umnikelo wakhe wokuzehlukanisela kwakhe eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, ngaphandle kwalokho isandla sakhe singafinyelela kukho\x + Levi 25.26.\x*; njengesithembiso sakhe asithembisileyo uzakwenza njalo, njengomlayo wobuNaziri bakhe.
\s Ukubusiswa kwabantu ngabapristi
\p
\v 22 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 23 Tshono kuAroni lakumadodana akhe uthi: Lizabusisa kanje abantwana bakoIsrayeli, lisithi kubo\x + Levi 9.22. Dute. 21.5. 1 Lan. 23.13.\x*:
\v 24 IN\nd kosi\nd* kayikubusise, ikulondoloze\x + Hlab. 121.7.\x*.
\v 25 IN\nd kosi\nd* kayikhanyise ubuso bayo kuwe\x + Hlab. 31.16; 67.1; 80.3,7,19; 119.135. Dan. 9.17.\x*, ibe lomusa kuwe\x + Gen. 43.29. Hlab. 67.1.\x*.
\v 26 IN\nd kosi\nd* kayiphakamise ubuso bayo kuwe, ikunike ukuthula.
\v 27 Ngokunjalo bazabeka ibizo lami phezu kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli, mina-ke ngizababusisa\x + Dute. 28.10. 2 Lan. 7.14. Isa. 43.7. Dan. 9.18,19.\x*.
